{"type": "excalidraw", "version": 2, "source": "excalidraw-diagram-skill", "elements": [{"type": "rectangle", "id": "darkbg", "x": -4000, "y": -3000, "width": 10000, "height": 7500, "backgroundColor": "#1e1e2e", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "transparent", "strokeWidth": 0, "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100}, {"type": "text", "id": "title1", "x": 20, "y": 10, "width": 456, "height": 28, "text": "✅ 안전 (복사)  ❌ 위험 (원본 변경)", "fontSize": 20, "strokeColor": "#e5e5e5", "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "center", "verticalAlign": "middle", "opacity": 100}, {"type": "rectangle", "id": "box2", "x": 20, "y": 45, "width": 456.5, "height": 228, "backgroundColor": "#1e3a5f", "fillStyle": "solid", "strokeColor": "#4a9eed", "strokeWidth": 2, "roughness": 1, "opacity": 100, "roundness": {"type": 3}}, {"type": "text", "id": "txt3", "x": 35, "y": 60, "width": 426, "height": 198, "text": ".map()  .push()  → [...arr, new]\n.filter()  .pop()  → .slice(0, -1)\n.slice()  .shift()  → .slice(1)\n.concat()  .unshift()  → [new, ...arr]\n[...spread]  .splice()  → .slice + 조합\n.toSorted() ★  .sort()  → [...arr].sort()\n.toReversed() ★  .reverse()  → [...arr].reverse()\n.toSpliced() ★  arr[i] = x  → .map()으로 교체\n★ ES2023 — 원본을 변경하지 않는 새 버전", "fontSize": 14, "strokeColor": "#e5e5e5", "fontFamily": 2, "textAlign": "left", "verticalAlign": "middle", "opacity": 100, "containerId": "box2"}], "appState": {"viewBackgroundColor": "#1e1e2e"}}